{"tid":2192841,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"［立法會去留爭議］弱勢社群是政治爭鬥的犧牲品","createTime":"2020-09-07T11:24:25.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-07T11:58:13.000Z","uid":325346,"like":2,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"471289ee9e223cee46f67877dfd31e9ab2b6d374","tid":2192841,"uid":325346,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-07T11:24:25.000Z","msg":"在之前初選睇到連登仔唔太支持工黨<br />\n嫌佢地左膠（阻膠）<br />\n但工黨係有做議題的政黨<br />\n南亞爸爸佢真係有幫殘疾人士爭取權益<br />\n唔能夠抹殺<br />\n社福界議員與南亞爸爸可以與受害人家屬開記者會<br />\n例如院舍問題、醫療失當<br />\n最近東區醫院有智障病人因為著約束衣而引致自殘、最後死亡、議員都有去信醫管局詢問，另外事件交左俾死因庭<br />\n<br />\n如果無議員邊個幫弱勢社群？<br />\n可能連登仔個個父母都健康、長命百歲無諗過相關問題<br />\n如果靠建制派去爭取、就食撚屎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n個人是反對委任派、要諗既係即使無議席「前議員」、「素人」建立的影子平台點樣幫到佢地？"},{"pid":"0b52ac25a8cccc85f43efd10f6393bae6b9b26d2","tid":2192841,"uid":146030,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-07T11:25:50.000Z","msg":"亂世仲講呢啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n民生嘢係太平盛世做"},{"pid":"b667837f76a787286a90e0d8c2d15e3b3f955739","tid":2192841,"uid":325346,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"0b52ac25a8cccc85f43efd10f6393bae6b9b26d2","tid":2192841,"uid":146030,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-07T11:25:50.000Z","msg":"亂世仲講呢啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n民生嘢係太平盛世做"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-07T11:33:03.000Z","msg":"亂世唔會病？手足唔會病？<br />\n手足斷腳都要過之後的生活"},{"pid":"d49230ab2f9c5b60b6f3e763b61a12cbb59c1619","tid":2192841,"uid":146030,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b667837f76a787286a90e0d8c2d15e3b3f955739","tid":2192841,"uid":325346,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"0b52ac25a8cccc85f43efd10f6393bae6b9b26d2","tid":2192841,"uid":146030,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-07T11:25